-> Products (sub category)
Troubleshooting Steps
How to use Bulk Import: Back office -> app store -> my apps -> setup. Download the stock sheet and update your stock using Excel or Google sheets. You can use any of these templates to your specified need. How to upload the CSV file(must be CSV, and it must be files that come to back office bulk import, no outside or home made templates.) -> upload your modified template -> download -> Import.

How to change pricing on multiple choice product groups?: back office -> MCPG-> details -> update prices.

How to update products?: Back office -> manage-> products (Depending on product list your on it be a button on left hand side that will say Edit or  just  double tap/click the screen to modify the prices on the pop up box line (horizontal line) or highlight blue line.) ( on the non classic product it be option on the right hand side, press the 3 dots. This is where you can duplicate products, delete products, etc.) ( columns and filters give you customization over how you can view the table.)

How to do anything else under the manage tab visit our YouTube channel: https://youtube.com/@eposnow?si=VBuelLZqmXKQfUf6


